node.title: Teenager dies in Omaha after being hit by car on New Year's Day
node.description: The driver of the car knew the teenager.
node.content:
["A teenager has died after being hit by a car in Omaha in the early hours of New Year's Day, police said in a statement. ", "The driver of the car, who is assisting police, was known to the deceased person. 
", "Emergency services were called to Omaha Drive at around 4am on Saturday morning. 
", "The Serious Crash Unit is investigating to establish the circumstances of how this tragedy has occurred.
", " "]
